	                        <div id="dsq-comment-message-2733786638" class="dsq-comment-message">
	                            <div id="dsq-comment-text-2733786638" class="dsq-comment-text">
	                                <p>Hey, Julian!</p><p>What about the second problem, it's difficult to understand from your message without proper formatting, but I was tricky and was able to see what's the problem :) You placed `anonymous` key under `logout` but should under your firewall name like:</p><p></p><pre><code><br>your_firewall_name:<br>    logout:<br>        path:   /logout<br>        target: /log_index<br>    anonymous:    true<br></code><br></pre><p></p><p>Please, fix it first and let me know if your first issue still exist.</p><p>Cheers!</p>
	                            </div>
